{
  "stem": "868.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now, these priests could have relieved their conscience by saying, we can help unfortunate people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we will help those that do not put us at-- at risk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Don't forget that Italy was being torn apart by two gigantic armies facing each other, fighting on its own soil.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Bombardments daily.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Everything was being blown to-- to bits.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There were hundreds of thousands of Italians, Christians, who were bombed out of their houses, living on the roads, living in-- where ever they-- they could.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was plenty of help they could've directed their attention to without risking their lives to help Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And if you help Jews, help Italian Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They speak the language.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They have connections.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We, the foreign Jews, didn't speak the language, had no money, no papers, no place to-- to live.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were the most vulnerable of-- of all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the most dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This plus the fact that we had no ration cards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We had to be fed, and food was very strictly rationed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There were sheets with 30 or 31 numbers in it, one for each day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And you cut off that little coupon, and you went to the grocer or to the baker, and you got your small ration.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But we had nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They took all these problems on their hands.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And always with compassion, not with resentment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "OK, we have to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And not in a superficial way, either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Here, we found you a hiding place, we've done our share.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Their concern was daily, deep, personal, and constant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And at no time did they try to convert us to Catholicism.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Now, you must remember that Catholic is a proselytizing religion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It's missionary.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "The object is to convert as many souls as possible to Catholicism.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
